      "text": "Ta patt buhs arridsan di-\ndefinits Galdeem buht / pee\nras Telts Puffes / prett See-\ni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ar fatwahm tschetrdefinits\naba Kahjahm / pa diwt Kah-\nn appakſch weena Galda / un\ni Kahjas appakſch ohtra\nda.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet us to TeltsPuffi prett\nkarn buhs tew fetchus Gal-\ntaitiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tew arridsan buhs diwi\ndus taitiht par Stuhru\ndeem / tahs Telts abbejos\nnds.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un teem buhs pa diweem\nafsch Gallâ falikteem buht /\nrridsan pa diweem Wirs-gal-\nweenu Rizki falikteem buht;\nirr tas watjaga ar teem diwi\ndeem / kas par Stuhra Gal-\nbuhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta buhs teem astonceim\nceem buht ar jawahm fudra-\nahjahm / tahs irr feschpa-\nits Kahjas/ diwi Kahjas ap-\nh ikweena Galda.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tew arri buhs zaurschau-\ns (Kahrtis) taitiht no Sit-\nKohka/ peezas pee teem Gal-\nweenâ Telts Puffê.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un peezas pee teem Gal-\nohtrâ Telts Puffê/ir peezas\nchaujamäs Kahrtis pee tahs\ns Galdeem abbejos Sahnôs\nWaffaru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tai widdejai zaurschauja-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhs tohs GalduS\nar Seltu pahrwilkt / un winno\nRinkus / (preekſch tahm zaurs-\nchaujamahm Kahrtim) no Sel-\nta taitiht/ tahs Kahrtis buhs tew\narridsan ar Seltu pahrwilkt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad buhs tew to Telti\nuszelt/ittinta/ ka tew Kalnâ rah-\ndihts irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz to buhs tew weenu\nPreekſchwelkamu taſiht no Pa-\nsilluma/ un Purpura/ un dahr-\nga Sarkanuna/ un faschkettina-\ntahm Dsibjahm / ar Padohmu\nbuhs tam darritam tapt ar Ke-\nrubim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhs winnu pa-\nkahrt pee tschetreem/ ar Seltu\npahrwilkteem Stabbeein no Sit-\ntim-Kohka / winna Kahfischeem\nbuhs no Selta buht / (un teem\nbuhs stahweht) us tschetr fu-\ndraba Kahjahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhs to Preekſch-\nwelkamo pee teem Kahfischeem pa-\nkahrt / un tahs Leezibas-Schkir-\nstu turp us Preekſchwelkama\nEskchu nest/ un fchim Preekſch-\nwelkamain buhs jums weena\nStarpiaba buht / starp to fwehtu/\nun starp to wiss fwehtaku Weetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhs to Salih-\ndsinachanas-Wahku us to Leezi-\nbas - Schkirstu eekſch tahs wifs-\nfwehtakas Weetas lift.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un to Galdu buhs tew\nahran to Preekſchwelkamo lift/un\n"
    }
  ],
